Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.61,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,Crap! Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.04,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:16.76,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.32,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,This isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.07,Sign,Kanji Title,0,0,0,,{\an8\b0\fscx100\fs40\fsp1\c&HF2F2F2&\blur0.6\pos(1087,564)}The Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.76,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Has everyone lost their minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.24,Default,Arita,0,0,0,,Mr. Chibiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.98,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,No one else escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:20.78,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.99,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,The bleeding has stopped. \NIt's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.74,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,You three stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.54,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.33,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Matsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.77,Default,Matsui,0,0,0,,Hel—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.00,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:50.02,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Do you remember this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.19,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.94,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Damn. Guess she wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.94,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You guess? What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:00.31,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Sugiura already said \Nthat it was Misaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.24,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,but you know, I think \Nyou're the dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.04,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,It all started this May, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:12.21,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Logically, whoever joined the class during May is the dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.13,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No! This all started in April!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.06,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,You think I'm going \Nto fall for that shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.28,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why... are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:44.96,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,I figured it out when \NTeshigawara tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:48.93,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,If I don't send the dead \Nback to death, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:49.79,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Still—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.95,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.54,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,If you hadn't transferred, \Nthen Yukari wouldn't have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.00,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,If only you hadn't talked \Nto that nonexistent girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.89,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,Send the dead back to—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:15.60,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You idiot. Kouichi isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:20.11,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You've killed two people, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.47,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.45,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I'll help you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.92,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Keep Yukari company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:36.67,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Classmates shouldn't do something as stupid as killing one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.14,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Big talk there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.90,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,but someone who ran to the sidelines\Nbecause he was afraid of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.30,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,has no right to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.87,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,While it's true I ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:52.27,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,I can still save a student who's about to die for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.71,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,A spectator like you \Ncan't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.84,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You can't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.61,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,The only ones who can fix this \Nare those living in death's jaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.49,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Get outside, Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.66,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.62,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.50,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.27,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.21,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,C'mon, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.28,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.14,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki! If you're here, \Nsay something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.75,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.77,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,We're all going to die if I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.44,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Even you could die—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No! Misaki's not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.99,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,If the calamity doesn't \Ncease after killing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.89,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,then I'll believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.38,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,This is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.04,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Why? I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.43,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to protect everyone! Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.71,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,If you really have a death wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.14,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,then I'll just kill you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.66,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.12,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:38.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.37,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.56,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not from Yomi North.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.89,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.49,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.28,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.58,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.16,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone I loved just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.37,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.54,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.00,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.94,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,A year and a half ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.47,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I hit you with an empty can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.00,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.96,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Goodness. You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:23.39,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Even if you don't, you're \Nsupposed to say you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.54,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Akazawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.69,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki!
